  "detailed_description": "When a massive and mysterious space station suddenly shows up, the Robot Exploration Squad is sent in to investigate. You play as the first scientist to throw on a robo suit and board the station.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nA 2D Metroidvania game with equal focus on action and exploration. The game features a massive open world, plenty of upgrades, diverse enemies, and huge bosses.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nAre you a bad enough robot to make it out in one piece?",
